>\n據了解當日12位港人早上在果洲群島附近等待台灣貨船接應，但遭到中方海警船越界拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n據郭卓堅覆述，海警曾警告會向12名港人開槍，整個過程歷時約一小時。<br />\n<br />\n而蝦艇當時位置比12位港人更近邊界，如果越界理應自己先被捕。另外，水警平日會在現場巡邏至早上十一時離開，但當日八時左右已離開現場，之後九點就發生12位港人被拘捕事件。<br />\n<br />\nThe arrest of 12 Hong Kong people at sea by mainland authorities was made by mainland coast guards that allegedly crossed the border near Ninepin Group, a nearby witness on a shrimp boat reported. The shrimp boat was located closer to the border than the 12 at the time of arrest.<br />\n<br />\nThe 12 Hong Kong people were waiting for a Taiwanese cargo ship. The mainland coast guards then approached and threatened them that they would open fire if they resist to cooperate. The event lasted about an hour until they are arrested, according to Kwok Cheuk-kin.<br />\n<br />\nAlso, the Hong Kong coast guards are often on patrol until 11 a.m. On that day, however, the guards left the patrol site at around 8 a.m. and arrested the 12 by the Mainland coast guards at 9 a.m."},{"pid":"e6671979e6eb4209cc953aa500d09b294afa92f8","tid":2204067,"uid":96327,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T19:41:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dLN8591.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdLN8591.jpg&h=e92c3e1b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aWyPQBK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaWyPQBK.jpg&h=238d95a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8f2a873fc7b9d66f6a267a10c3264335bf663a2","tid":2204067,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6671979e6eb4209cc953aa500d09b294afa92f8","tid":2204067,"uid":96327,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T19:41:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dLN8591.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdLN8591.jpg&h=e92c3e1b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aWyPQBK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaWyPQBK.jpg&h=238d95a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T19:42:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19435ec7b080f0de1d0ef24fea91f7a082efdb0f","tid":2204067,"uid":289486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4571f8575630ad2beb84e6b6752ca28e5de22001","tid":2204067,"uid":56243,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T19:30:20.000Z","msg":"乜香港省返祖國都叫偷渡咩？ 哦～ 港獨！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T21:02:33.000Z","msg":"真，想講好耐，佢地居然話中國人由中國偷渡去中國，第一次理清事實真相嘅時候唔小心笑左出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a267202be27d9f6fa274d12f86db7de5974c2f17","tid":2204067,"uid":158888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T21:36:59.000Z","msg":"支那最叻搬龍門<br />\n12個人去台灣<br />\n乜台灣唔係中國一部分咩<br />\n咁點算偷渡"},{"pid":"20cb8cf540089d016cc9f2ec8b233ab6dff88e5a","tid":2204067,"uid":245849,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"db4aaf00f2fb5026792979f437df50667d36e892","tid":2204067,"uid":9315,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T19:12:22.000Z","msg":"上面玩人治  黨話點就點架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T21:47:36.000Z","msg":"要救手足，只有戰爭"},{"pid":"6d512f84ca0f589b736acb937a30944fc86e23eb","tid":2204067,"uid":17103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T23:25:08.000Z","msg":"中國䟙你咩罪根本唔重要，全世界都知道佢老屈。之前個靚仔被屈嫖妓，有無人真係話佢真係嫖？無人信大家都想佢儘快離開去安全地方。<br />\n<br />\n事實上中國係有分境內外，所以係有邊防。香港政府話過香港市民有權自由唔經管制站出境。呢次擺明就係有鬼賣撚咗呢班人，再捉佢去大陸祭旗。<br />\n<br />\n過去香港逃犯着草返大陸都係就咁移交返香港。而家中國借偷渡捉佢再諗住䟙顛覆國家生豬肉。過去最高判廿一年，平均 3-7 年。<br />\n<br />\n所以你點討論分析有冇離開香港，中國境係無用，洗頭艇擺到明落嚟拉人。大家都無奈 &ldquo;接受&rdquo; 因為香港政府從來唔係為香港市民而係傀儡。<br />\n<br />\n而家要嘅係儘快釋放落返嚟同埋點搞掂等佢哋自由。"},{"pid":"bb791cb05c57a286c5bc3cd9a89d3f5159130a17","tid":2204067,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T01:30:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35224ff489483d685d9bc1a15821a0b22be04d7b","tid":2204067,"uid":47210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4571f8575630ad2beb84e6b6752ca28e5de22001","tid":2204067,"uid":56243,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T19:30:20.000Z","msg":"乜香港省返祖國都叫偷渡咩？ 哦～ 港獨！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T02:15:09.000Z","msg":"諗到charge呢條罪嗰個先係&quot;企圖將香港從中国分裂出去&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<code>寧化飛灰\n不作浮塵\n光復香港\n時代革命</code>"},{"pid":"458d6ad80db90b8d538621729f7814b839d583fd","tid":2204067,"uid":313615,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T02:27:40.000Z","msg":"唔畀睇家屬律師，官派律師做樣，都係為咗單獨審訊12港人過程中，得到佢哋國安法犯罪情報，告另外嘅罪名。"},{"pid":"df3d0a2968d8ca4646c0408595c459d63659080c","tid":2204067,"uid":334957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2a8512a961f7cab1dc333afe0bf72fe200d934a8","tid":2204067,"uid":100772,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T19:10:31.000Z","msg":"我記得之前有條中國佬唔記得落車黎左香港 仲護送佢返去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T02:28:50.000Z","msg":"係西九落車行狗鐵隧道<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58ddc5b4e759984bc292c75e3edb793bc5c868e6","tid":2204067,"uid":313615,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a8512a961f7cab1dc333afe0bf72fe200d934a8","tid":2204067,"uid":100772,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T19:10:31.000Z","msg":"我記得之前有條中國佬唔記得落車黎左香港 仲護送佢返去"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T02:30:02.000Z","msg":"遣返佢返內地"},{"pid":"4148f3cb06075450003efa646cf41a93141c9ae1","tid":2204067,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T02:34:38.000Z","msg":"好呀<br />\n你自己落到黎香港唔拎證入到境試下"},{"pid":"48a3fa374c93768d4e3ac61531baa459d0358433","tid":2204067,"uid":313615,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4148f3cb06075450003efa646cf41a93141c9ae1","tid":2204067,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T02:34:38.000Z","msg":"好呀<br />\n你自己落到黎香港唔拎證入到境試下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T02:44:00.000Z","msg":"佢都冇辦法離開邊境，中國有邊防，律師係國家工作人員，佢哋被邊控，出境前會被邊防攔。每次都要事先佢哋個人申請「申請去邊度 幾天」，佢哋公司人力資源部批准 擔保，公安局出入境解除備案，佢哋先可以出境「公務員 銀行 國企職員都係咁」"},{"pid":"59ec1e69c51c45ffb2224ec74cb68e3cfe081197","tid":2204067,"uid":263349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T02:46:15.000Z","msg":"即係香港同中國唔應該有邊境 <br />\n<br />\n如果一大批中國人偷渡入境唔係犯法 可以接受？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家個問題係 可能係中共<br />\n<br />\n係香港境非法拉人 在先 理應比返香港審 <br />\n<br />\n而且被捕嘅人無得到法律保障 先係重點"}]}